data.description: This 3-bedroom, 2-Full Bath home with fenced backyard is waiting for you! Tucked away on a quiet street, custom landscaping greets you as you arrive . The Open Floor Plan allows lots of natural light and the Den and Living/Dining room area are perfect for entertaining. The Roof was placed in 2013 as well as the Hot Water Tank, Downspouts and Siding.  The Main Level Primary Bedroom is spacious with wood floors and double closets! The 2nd level has 2 bedrooms, a Full Tub/Shower Bath, and Floored Eaves for plenty of storage. The Lower Level has one finished room that could be another bedroom or hobby room. The lower level workshop is heated and cooled with direct access to the backyard. There is plenty of space for a garden and play equipment!
